{"title":"“鞭打春牛”","authors":["朱相如"],"dates":[{"year":1997,"month":2,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"“鞭打春牛”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朱相如"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年年以新枝刺绣人间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年年用嫩叶点绿潮头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年年田野里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那春天第一只牛蹄窝里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总是盛满了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼的希冀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心的祈求……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遥远的习俗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被时光透进"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天的风景潮流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随便站在哪座立交桥上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都可浸进那古老意蕴的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深远和丰厚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽然追逐春光的牛蹄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已为飞轮切换"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但春牛的图腾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依然是一脉东方精神的源头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼前的一条条高速公路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不正是一条条通向春天的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犁沟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"且不说开犁后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行将涵盖生活所有过程的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种与收"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那清脆的鞭花儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正雷火般地滚过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笋起的厂房和高楼"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}